Innocent, Bishop‚ servant of the servants of God, to his venerable brother Bernard, Bishop of st. David’s, health and apostolieal benediction. Our venerable brother Ur- ban, Bishop of Llandaff, for the obtaining of justice to his Ohumh, carne twice with great fatigue to the apostolical See. And afterwards he was summoned by our predeces- sor, of blesaed memory‚ Pope Honorius, that at the next festival of St. Lulre he should come to the apostolical See to answer thee respecting tha diocesan boundaries.
